An accidental firing?

31:54.880 --> 31:57.201
Yeah, but not the one
that you'd expect.

31:57.240 --> 32:00.243
The prosecution was correct.

32:00.280 --> 32:03.044
The shot came from
three feet away.

32:03.080 --> 32:05.446
The weapon was
in the drawer

32:05.490 --> 32:07.287
of your client's bureau.

32:07.320 --> 32:08.685
Heather was a thief,

32:08.720 --> 32:09.755
and when Bianca was
in the bathroom,

32:09.790 --> 32:13.055
Heather checked the drawer
for valuables, money.

32:13.090 --> 32:14.694
Oh, my God.

32:14.730 --> 32:16.652
She checked the drawer
with the weapon...

32:18.300 --> 32:20.063
