32:25.640 --> 32:28.108
The shot was fired
from three feet away,

32:28.140 --> 32:29.368
but vertically,
not horizontally.

32:29.410 --> 32:32.004
And it was accidentally
fired by Heather.

32:32.050 --> 32:33.244
There's no service
In here.

32:33.280 --> 32:34.372
And once it
was ﬁred,

