37:55.540 --> 37:56.598
Watch me.

37:56.640 --> 37:58.699
Watch us.

37:58.740 --> 38:00.833
There's nothing going on
with Alicia.

38:03.110 --> 38:04.941
(chuckles)

38:06.110 --> 38:07.941
Turn out the lights.

38:26.100 --> 38:28.933
