40:06.870 --> 40:07.996
Hey, Doc,

40:08.030 --> 40:10.692
you look depleted.

40:10.740 --> 40:12.958
(chuckles)
I guess I am.

40:13.010 --> 40:14.102
I don't know.

40:14.140 --> 40:17.701
I sit here listening
to everybody talk,

40:17.740 --> 40:21.540
and I just feel like we weren't
given enough information.

40:25.790 --> 40:29.556
So what do we do?

40:31.260 --> 40:35.151
Do you have
reasonable doubt?

40:37.230 --> 40:39.869
I don't know.

40:39.900 --> 40:42.494
I just have...

40:42.540 --> 40:44.428
reasonable ignorance.

40:59.550 --> 41:01.245
Kalinda,
we've got a problem.

41:01.290 --> 41:03.758
The bailiff's warning
that the verdict's coming in.

41:03.790 --> 41:04.654
Okay.

41:04.690 --> 41:06.829
Bianca and her mother
want to talk to us.

41:06.860 --> 41:07.827
Oh, no.

41:07.860 --> 41:09.020
Yep. Where's Cary?
We need Cary.

41:09.060 --> 41:09.890
Why?

41:09.930 --> 41:11.989
She likes him.
Maybe he can talk to her.

41:12.030 --> 41:13.122
Okay.

41:16.540 --> 41:18.963
Okay...

41:19.010 --> 41:19.965
We're unanimous.

41:20.010 --> 41:21.102
Oh!
Yes!

41:21.140 --> 41:23.904
Finally. Good job.

41:23.940 --> 41:25.544
Democracy in action.

41:25.580 --> 41:28.572
All for $15 a day.

41:28.620 --> 41:30.872
I bet a lot of jurors trade
numbers and say

41:30.920 --> 41:32.785
