42:02.320 --> 42:03.309
No, I'm sorry, I'm not.

42:03.350 --> 42:04.908
This happens sometimes

42:04.950 --> 42:08.954
when one side or the other
worries about the outcome.

42:08.990 --> 42:11.049
So again, thank you.

42:11.090 --> 42:13.957
